title: (x) Techno style sans with open g - Infinity {Stephen}
content:
I received a request for an ID on this, and I haven't been able to find it. This 'g' looks very familiar, but T-26, Psy/Ops and Veer's 'Techno' fonts didn't turn it up.   
   
Anyone recognize it? Thanks   
 ![Techno w/open g](http://web.archive.org/web/20050516054750im_/http:/www.typophile.com/forums/messages/83/69131.jpg)
author: bowfinpw

comments.content: Thanks Stephen, that's it all right.
